      <akn:section eId="sec_21_2113">
        <akn:num>21-2113</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Construction of power relating to personal and family maintenance.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_21-2113_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>In a statutory power of attorney the language granting power with respect to personal and family maintenance empowers the agent to:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_21-2113_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>For the purposes of this section, the term “domestic partner” shall have the same meaning as provided in § 32-701(3).</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
